{"tid":1317587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東: 傷其十指不如斷其一指","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:47:33.000Z","uid":255402,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"354d1e082d4d1ceaa341a8e03a032ef1c5bbd0f3","tid":1317587,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:37:02.000Z","msg":"<code>打&ldquo;殲滅戰&rdquo;是毛澤東的拿手好戲。在敵強我弱的情況下，和敵人硬拚就如同乞丐和龍王比寶，&ldquo;擊潰戰，對於雄厚之敵不是基本上決定勝負的東西。而殲滅戰，則對任何敵人都立即起了重大影響&rdquo;。擊潰敵人，即使有可能把敵人打跑了，但敵人的有生力量還存在，他就會重新反撲過來，對我們仍然是威脅。殲滅戰則是把敵人全部地消滅或俘虜，一個也不能讓他跑了。這樣，那怕殲滅的是很小的一部分敵人，敵人的力量也因之削弱了一部分。所以毛澤東說：&ldquo;對於人，傷其十指不如斷其一指；對於敵，擊潰其十個師不如殲滅其一個師。&rdquo;</code>"},{"pid":"364cb9cef2bedc1ac4a2938edf548e4c4a2a5437","tid":1317587,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba49e6bc0851f5b2c9db67a50f2e7d6ebd99871","tid":1317587,"uid":269991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c04c36acf18b2f65cab7241196a5c4d2d5ac4e","tid":1317587,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b64b3c072cc9cba3e11c06ff2609dc14a71ebb","tid":1317587,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:18:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輿論工作要立即展開！<br />\n唔好比同溫層欺騙！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>黑警挖示威者眼先被咬斷手指</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1317565/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1317565/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>黑警拗斷被捕人士手腕</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1316051/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1316051/page/1</